                  Her ex attack is very good: it stays on the screen for extended times up to 3 bounces (green, yellow, red colors indicate respectively 3, 2, 1 remaining bounces).
                  Its direction is rather unpredictable despite the "bouncing behavior" and it blocks hits. However, it can be swung outside of the field with a L1
